description: With your app, this agent allows users to manage their apps and app settings. This is ideal for hand-free situations and can help when your app has a more complex UI. Instead of tapping around for what they need, users can just ask.
shortDescription: Manage your applications, user controlled settings, and preferences
examples:
User: Could you launch Spotify please?
User: I want to download Vine from the Play Store.
User: Update all my apps.
User: Search for a new music player app.
User: Open Notifications settings.
User: What can this app do?
User: Clear history.
User: Can you show me your voice settings?
